gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Bucks 112, Timberwolves 107
gameRecap.excerpt: The Bucks defeated the Timberwolves, 112-107. Giannis Antetokounmpo led the Bucks with 33 points, 13 rebounds, and five assists, while Damian Lillard added 21 points, 10 assists, and nine rebounds in the victory. Anthony Edwards tallied 28 points, nine rebounds, and five assists for the Timberwolves in the losing effort. The Bucks improve to 36-21, while the Timberwolves fall to 39-17.
